OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA wet start to the morning, but
OL,6,Frain quickly clearing to the east.
OL,7,FThen a day of sunshine and scattered
OL,8,Fblustery showers. Some of the showers
OL,9,Fwill be heavy, with hail and thunder.
OL,10,FFeeling chilly with a gusty
OL,11,Fsouthwesterly wind.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FStaying windy, with further
OL,14,Fshowers through the evening and
OL,15,Fovernight. Again, some of these will
OL,16,Fbe on the heavy side, with the risk of
OL,17,Fhail.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
