OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FAnother day of sunny spells
OL,6,Fand scattered showers is expected.
OL,7,FShowers may be a little less frequent
OL,8,Fthen Saturday. Winds remaining brisk,
OL,9,Fthough gradually easing later in the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,13,FSunshine and showers through Monday.
OL,14,FDrier and brighter on Tuesday, ahead
OL,15,Fof rain arriving later in the day.
OL,16,FWetter and windier again on Wednesday.
OL,17,FTemperatures trending up a little.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
